South African Labor Union Solidarity Declares Dispute With Telkom Over Pay

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-06-24T13:58:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-24/south-african-labor-union-solidarity-declares-dispute-with-telkom-over-pay.html
South African labor union Solidarity
said it declared a wage dispute with Telkom South Africa Ltd.  Telkom is offering workers a 4.5 percent increase while the
labor union wants 10 percent, Solidarity said in an e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  